{"tid":653895,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"進軍法國！巴黎小米之家 5 月 22 日揭幕","createTime":"2018-05-05T06:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T05:52:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3028759679c7a6f2781ba3f4c8d3605268cc7503","tid":653895,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:46:57.000Z","msg":"唐美鳳<br />\n<br />\n香港首間小米之家地舖日前揭幕，地點位於旺角創興中心，佔地超過 3,600 平方呎。早前宣佈夥拍長和進軍歐洲市場的小米，除了在香港開設新零售點，亦會在本月 22 日於法國開設小米之家零售店，這是繼去年 11 月在西班牙開店後，小米再次進軍西歐國家。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5 月 22 日揭幕的法國首間小米之家將會設在時尚之都巴黎，小美表示稍後還會在法國其他城市開店。法國的小米之家將會銷售品牌的智能電話，亦會發售小米生態圈的其他產品，包括電動滑板車、智能家居、相機等產品。在日前跟長和合組策略聯盟的發佈，小米表示會透過對方的電訊和零售網絡，將手機和其他智能產品帶到歐洲，可以肯定將來會在更多歐洲國家見到小米之家的影蹤。"},{"pid":"6d4b629265db1214c30c6a9fe3b49dc6986eafe8","tid":653895,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"羞家羞到去法國"},{"pid":"0b1826c6838304f4a1c8ed9293697d681361b84f","tid":653895,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:48:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/05/mi-home-opens-in-paris-may-22/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2Fmi-home-opens-in-paris-may-22%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=FEX5tlkpPGC2vXGalhBCLL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=d5f7a131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/05/mi-home-opens-in-paris-may-22/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n打擊華為中興變相益咗小米，今次小米番身有望了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08687a1f685747ce4856d28e373a6ef5e47400d4","tid":653895,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fe33a29dc91efc0cf0d4fbe777a92eaa0ed21f","tid":653895,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislik